comment: Antic (ATL) and Williams (BKN) briefly engage after Antic sets the screen on the perimeter.
Williams (BKN) trips Teague (ATL) on his drive to the basket.
Teague (ATL) does not gain possession after the blocked shot by Millsap (ATL) and the shot clock is incorrectly reset.
Lopez (BKN) and Teague (ATL) make incidental contact with one another as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Lopez (BKN) jumps in the air and lands before passing the ball.
Bogdanovic (BKN) does not affect Millsap's (ATL) RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Young (BKN) is in legal guarding position and does not affect Millsap's (ATL) RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Young (BKN) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Millsap (ATL) on the catch and move to the basket.
Antic (ATL) maintains legal guarding position and Young (BKN) loses control of the ball on his own as he attempts the layup.
Lopez (BKN) clamps Antic's (ATL) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Carroll (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Lopez' (BKN) layup attempt.
Antic (ATL) sets the screen on Bogdanovic (BKN) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Antic (ATL) establishes legal guarding position as Bogdanovic (BKN) loses the ball while attempting the spin move.
Carroll (ATL) makes contact with Lopez' (BKN) arm and the contact affects his movement to the basket and layup attempt.
Horford (ATL) clamps Lopez' (BKN) arm during rebounding.
Lopez (BKN) does not push Carroll (ATL) and the contact between Carroll and Johnson (BKN) is incidental.
Millsap (ATL) makes contact with Young's (BKN) body on the jump shot.
Horford (ATL) sets the screen on Anderson (BKN) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Anderson (BKN) holds Millsap (ATL) and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Williams (BKN) makes incidental contact with Carroll (ATL) during rebounding.
The contact by Millsap (ATL) on Williams (BKN) affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Korver (ATL) commits a take foul on Johnson (BKN).
